<subSubSection pageId="82" pageNumber="361" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="82.[127,1335,1748,2492]" pageId="82" pageNumber="361">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[129,478,2300,2333]" pageId="82" pageNumber="361">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Critically Endangered on The IUCN Red List owing to an extent of occurrence lower than 100 km®. Few records exist. Desert region of Perote has been modified recently to fields of maize and maguey.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
